20:10.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541073b78c91a7f508c6aaf066bac79115eb1228","tid":1929144,"uid":183058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"nese 係有眨意，係白人社會用嚟稱呼次等民族用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2f71965d194f26ee18bb7a4c5f13eeb8ee72a7","tid":1929144,"uid":252091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"Hongkonger有啲唔係咁好發音同唔夠響，<br />\nHongkongian四個音節，重音响kong度就易讀同響亮好多"},{"pid":"484a4fe15e7fdea7dd2303f0b1dbe51b79e0c104","tid":1929144,"uid":183058,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.linglish.net/extra/chinese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linglish.net%2Fextra%2Fchinese%2F&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4b853ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.linglish.net/extra/chinese/</a><br />\n<br />\n在英語中，英國人用後綴&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;來表示那些他們認為&ldquo;低等的&rdquo;、&ldquo;不重要的&rdquo;、&ldquo;弱小的&rdquo;、&ldquo;怪異的&rdquo;、&ldquo;帶有疾病的&rdquo;、&ldquo;從蟲子演變而來的&rdquo;種族；他們蔑視和厭惡這些種族。這些種族包括中國人　(Chinese)、日本人 (Japanese)、越南人 (Vietnamese) 、葡萄牙人 (Portuguese)。他們用&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;來羞辱我們。<br />\n<br />\n同時他們用後綴&ldquo;-an&rdquo;來表示那些所謂&ldquo;優等&rdquo;的種族，例如美國人 (American)、加拿大人 (Canadian)、英國人 (Britain)、德國人 (German)、加州人 (Californian)、德州人 (Texan)。<br />\n<br />\n這就是為什麼那個一文不值的流浪漢居然叫我&ldquo;Your Chinese&rdquo;，而不是&ldquo;Your Asian&rdquo;；&ldquo;Your American&rdquo;或&ldquo;Your Korean&rdquo;來侮辱我，盡管他根本不知道我是從哪裡來的。他需要使用一個羞辱我、傷害我的蔑語，這裡&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;就正好可以用於傷害任何黃種人。<br />\n<br />\n那麼&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;的字面意思是什麼呢?&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;表示小的、微小的和不重要的，&ldquo;China&rdquo;的意思是堅硬的粘土或泥土，那麼放在一起&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;就是用堅硬的粘土或泥土制成的微小的、微不足道的、怪異的東西。這真是一個莫大的侮辱！！<br />\n<br />\n我來自東亞，在那裡英國人曾經去過，征服、壓迫和羞辱過那裡的人民，並且把那個地方叫做&ldquo;China&rdquo;，把那裡的&ldquo;弱小的&rdquo;、&ldquo;劣等&rdquo;、&ldquo;分文不值&rdquo;、&ldquo;帶有疾病的&rdquo;、&ldquo;蟲子一樣的&rdquo;的人叫做&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;，盡管他們知道我們的土地的名字叫做&ldquo;中央之國&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"e63d61dd519786d80a2db84a43df6694f176a998","tid":1929144,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"Hongkonger  康狂牙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHongkan 康勤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957fc977f1741dc80bf1f46d84732def588f567a","tid":1929144,"uid":159413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5108c3a9bd2f912bcbecc17add15a721895ca0af","tid":1929144,"uid":16846,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"56f3e0ab0739d21d92e0fb5850c67c63d7d1f3a6","tid":1929144,"uid":343574,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:02:19.000Z","msg":"hongkonger有負面意思，est比較好，無詳細研究 之前大專英文老師講的"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:16:15.000Z","msg":"我老母話ese有負面意思，ian比較好，可惜都係冇詳細研究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:19:30.000Z","msg":"明明就係諷刺緊口頭話某某權威人士點講點講<br />\n#11 #12做乜撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34f545db70f704e918ba05855febae7868044c8","tid":1929144,"uid":16846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"484a4fe15e7fdea7dd2303f0b1dbe51b79e0c104","tid":1929144,"uid":183058,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.linglish.net/extra/chinese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linglish.net%2Fextra%2Fchinese%2F&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4b853ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.linglish.net/extra/chinese/</a><br />\n<br />\n在英語中，英國人用後綴&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;來表示那些他們認為&ldquo;低等的&rdquo;、&ldquo;不重要的&rdquo;、&ldquo;弱小的&rdquo;、&ldquo;怪異的&rdquo;、&ldquo;帶有疾病的&rdquo;、&ldquo;從蟲子演變而來的&rdquo;種族；他們蔑視和厭惡這些種族。這些種族包括中國人　(Chinese)、日本人 (Japanese)、越南人 (Vietnamese) 、葡萄牙人 (Portuguese)。他們用&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;來羞辱我們。<br />\n<br />\n同時他們用後綴&ldquo;-an&rdquo;來表示那些所謂&ldquo;優等&rdquo;的種族，例如美國人 (American)、加拿大人 (Canadian)、英國人 (Britain)、德國人 (German)、加州人 (Californian)、德州人 (Texan)。<br />\n<br />\n這就是為什麼那個一文不值的流浪漢居然叫我&ldquo;Your Chinese&rdquo;，而不是&ldquo;Your Asian&rdquo;；&ldquo;Your American&rdquo;或&ldquo;Your Korean&rdquo;來侮辱我，盡管他根本不知道我是從哪裡來的。他需要使用一個羞辱我、傷害我的蔑語，這裡&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;就正好可以用於傷害任何黃種人。<br />\n<br />\n那麼&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;的字面意思是什麼呢?&ldquo;-ese&rdquo;表示小的、微小的和不重要的，&ldquo;China&rdquo;的意思是堅硬的粘土或泥土，那麼放在一起&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;就是用堅硬的粘土或泥土制成的微小的、微不足道的、怪異的東西。這真是一個莫大的侮辱！！<br />\n<br />\n我來自東亞，在那裡英國人曾經去過，征服、壓迫和羞辱過那裡的人民，並且把那個地方叫做&ldquo;China&rdquo;，把那裡的&ldquo;弱小的&rdquo;、&ldquo;劣等&rdquo;、&ldquo;分文不值&rdquo;、&ldquo;帶有疾病的&rdquo;、&ldquo;蟲子一樣的&rdquo;的人叫做&ldquo;Chinese&rdquo;，盡管他們知道我們的土地的名字叫做&ldquo;中央之國&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國&rdquo;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原文摘自<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49e6b02101009qmt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_49e6b02101009qmt.html&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=c45f3ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49e6b02101009qmt.html</a> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n2020年喇，仲幫支那狗散播propaganda，上網查下etymology有咁難？"},{"pid":"2e5116a1a5ef38e2516480550ac3c60066002015","tid":1929144,"uid":305607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"之前都見到有人開po討論過用邊隻字好，包括有：<br />\n1. Hongkonger<br />\n2. Hongkongese<br />\n3. Hongkongian<br />\n<br />\n大家對唔同叫法各有原因，例如歷史、Grammar等，但覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候要統一一個叫法</span></span>。我係見我地自己人、外國新聞等大部分媒體都用Hongkonger，基本上已經用慣左，所以建議大家直接繼續用，無謂轉黎轉去。"},{"pid":"5ba6f0cefc2fed015fbc14d196e5cafc9efd1046","tid":1929144,"uid":92565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.linglish.n